  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Three Doses of Oral Fluticasone Propionate in Adults With Eosinophilic Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Study, Multicentre, Parallel, Double-blind, Randomized for the Dose to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Three Doses of Oral Fluticasone Propionate Compared to Placebo in Adults With Eosinophilic Esophagitis</official_title>
