  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of three doses of fluticasone
      propionate oral (viscous suspension) on changes of eosinophilic infiltration in esophageal
      biopsies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
